   "line": 3525,
   "endLine": 3538,
   "source": "<ROUTINE PRINT-OPEN-WINDOWS (\"AUX\" (FLR 3))\n\t <REPEAT ()\n\t\t <TELL \"on the \" <GET ,CARDINALS .FLR> \" floor, \">\n\t\t <COND (<L? <GET ,APT-DIR <+ <* <- .FLR 2> 12> 8>> 0>\n\t\t\t<TELL \"near the middle\">)\n\t\t       (T\n\t\t\t<TELL \"at the northern end\">)>\n\t\t <TELL \" of the building\">\n\t\t <COND (<G? <SET FLR <+ .FLR 1>> 5>\n\t\t\t<RETURN>)\n\t\t       (<EQUAL? .FLR 5>\n\t\t\t<TELL \", and \">)\n\t\t       (T\n\t\t\t<TELL \", \">)>>>"
