   "line": 3542,
   "endLine": 3558,
   "source": "<ROUTINE PICK-OPEN-WINDOWS (\"AUX\" (FLR 3) NUM H)\n\t <SETG SNIPER-FLOOR <+ <RANDOM 3> 2>>\n\t <REPEAT ()\n\t\t <PUT ,APT-DIR\n\t\t      <SET NUM <+ <* <- .FLR 2> 12>\n\t\t\t\t  <COND (<PROB 50>\n\t\t\t\t\t <SET H ,HALL-3>\n\t\t\t\t\t 8)\n\t\t\t\t\t(T\n\t\t\t\t\t <SET H ,HALL-4>\n\t\t\t\t\t 4)>>>\n\t\t      <- 0 <GET ,APT-DIR .NUM>>>\n\t\t <COND (<EQUAL? .FLR ,SNIPER-FLOOR>\n\t\t\t<SETG SNIPER-HALL .H>\n\t\t\t<PUT ,APT-DIR <- .NUM 1> 0>)>\n\t\t <COND (<G? <SET FLR <+ .FLR 1>> 5>\n\t\t\t<RETURN>)>>>\t "
