   "line": 3566,
   "endLine": 3575,
   "source": "<ROUTINE FILL-VACANCIES (\"AUX\" MAX (CNT 5) RND)\n\t <SET MAX </ <GET ,APT-DIR 0> 2>>\n\t <REPEAT ()\n\t\t  <COND (<L? <SET CNT <- .CNT 1>> 0>\n\t\t\t <RETURN>)>\n\t\t  <SET RND <RANDOM .MAX>>\n\t\t  <COND (<NOT <L? <GET ,APT-DIR <* .RND 2>> 0>>\n\t\t\t <PUT ,APT-DIR <- <* .RND 2> 1> 0>)\n\t\t\t(T\n\t\t\t <SET CNT <+ .CNT 1>>)>>>"
