   "source": "<ROUTINE PICK-WRONG-BUMPER (\"AUX\" TMP)\n\t <REPEAT ()\n\t\t <COND (<NOT <EQUAL? <SET TMP <PICK-ONE ,BUMPERS>> ,CONTACT>>\n\t\t\t<RETURN .TMP>)>>>"
