   "file": "good.zil",
   "line": 266,
   "endLine": 272,
   "source": "<ROUTINE BODY-PARTS-F ()\n\t <COND (<AND <VERB? PUT-ON> <EQUAL? ,PRSI ,BODY-PARTS>>\n\t\t<TELL\n\"You couldn't hide anything there.\" CR>)\n\t       (T\n\t\t<TELL\n\"There's no reason to refer to that part of your body.\" CR>)>>"
