   "source": "<ROUTINE IN-GUARD-VIEW? (\"AUX\" (MT <MOD ,CLOCK-TIME 360>))\n\t <COND (<AND <GUARDS-FACING-PLAYER?>\n\t\t     <L? <GUARD-DISTANCE> 86>>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)>>"
