   "source": "<ROUTINE YES? (\"OPTIONAL\" (TO-PERSON <>))\n\t <COND (.TO-PERSON\n\t\t<PRINTI \">>\">)\n\t       (T\n\t\t<PRINTI \">\">)>\n\t <PUTB ,P-INBUF 1 0>\n\t <READ ,P-INBUF ,P-LEXV>\n\t <COND (<YES-WORD? <GET ,P-LEXV 1>>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<EQUAL? <GET ,P-LEXV 1> ,W?N ,W?NO>\n\t\t<RFALSE>)\n\t       (<EQUAL? .TO-PERSON ,BAD-SPY>\n\t\t<TELL \"\\\"Please, just a simple yes or no.\\\"\">\n\t\t<CRLF>\n\t\t<CRLF>\n\t\t<AGAIN>)\n\t       (T\n\t\t<TELL \"Please answer YES or NO.\">)>\n\t\t<CRLF>\n\t\t<CRLF>\n\t        <AGAIN>>"
