   "source": "<ROUTINE V-REPLACE ()\n\t <COND (<AND <NOT ,PRSI>\n\t\t     <EQUAL? ,PRSO ,PEN-CAP>>\n\t\t<PERFORM ,V?PUT-ON ,PEN-CAP ,EXPLODING-PEN>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (T\n\t\t<TELL\n\"You'll have to say what to put the \" D ,PRSO \" in.\" CR>)>>"
