   "endLine": 2035,
   "source": "<ROUTINE FLUSH-BAD-SCENARIO (SC \"AUX\" F N)\n\t <SET F <FIRST? ,PROTAGONIST>>\n\t <REPEAT ()\n\t\t <COND (<ZERO? .F> <RETURN>)\n\t\t       (T\n\t\t\t<SET N <NEXT? .F>>\n\t\t\t<COND (<AND <GETP .F ,P?SCENARIO>\n\t\t\t\t    <NOT <EQUAL? <GETP .F ,P?SCENARIO> .SC>>>\n\t\t\t       ;<TELL CR \"[Flushing \" D .F \"]\">\n\t\t\t       <REMOVE .F>)>\n\t\t\t<SET F .N>)>>\n\t ;<TELL CR \"[Chapter Flushed/ RETURN to continue]\" CR>\n\t ;<INPUT 1>>"
