  "ALLEY-OOPS": {
   "name": "ALLEY-OOPS",
   "kind": "global",
   "file": "bad.zil",
   "line": 2131,
   "value": "\"You press through the crowd until you reach Ostnitz Street at a point\nwhere a street vendor is busily cleaning up his overturned cart. Soda\ncans and pretzels lie everywhere, making the congestion even worse than\nit was before. Behind the cart, to the west, is a blind alley sandwiched\nbetween the apartment building to your north and the office building to\nyour south. It might take a while to get there, though, with all the mess\nin the way.\""
  },
