  "BAD-END": {
   "name": "BAD-END",
   "kind": "global",
   "file": "bystander.zil",
   "line": 2435,
   "value": "\"\"I am afraid you have not been very honest\nwith us. We will need to ask some, how to say, more difficult\nquestions now.\" He motions to the guards, who lead you into a\nholding area nearby. After hours of questioning, you are\nfinally released, but not before missing your rendezvous.\""
  },
  "EPILOGUE-ASS": {
   "name": "EPILOGUE-ASS",
   "kind": "global",
   "file": "bystander.zil",
   "line": 2442,
   "value": "\"Epilogue|\n|\nTwo days later, in your hotel room in Vienna, you notice the headline\nreporting the assassination of the American ambassador to Litzenburg in\nthe small border town of Ostnitz. The apparent assassin\nwas a member of a radical Islamic group, although details of the plot\nmay never be known since the assassin himself was found dead at the\nscene of the crime, an apparent suicide.\""
  },
